Termination
. If
Customer concludes, based on its current or intended use of the Services, that
the Data Transfer Solution and/or SCCs, as applicable, do not provide
appropriate safeguards for Customer Personal Data, then Customer may immediately
terminate the Agreement for convenience by notifying Google in writing.
