. Information about Google and/or its
Affiliates' adoption of, or certification under, a Data Transfer Solution can be
found at https://policies.google.com/privacy/frameworks. The parties acknowledge
that Google has certified under the Data Privacy Framework on behalf of itself
and certain wholly-owned US subsidiaries. Google's certification is available at
https://www.dataprivacyframework.gov. The Data Privacy Framework will apply to
any Restricted European Transfer to a certified Google entity in the US.
